Reasoning: The paper deals with scheduling of a common resource between several concurrent users in a wireless channel, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also considers the feasibility of transmission rates, which involves information theory (cs.IT). The stability analysis and optimization of the system can be categorized under control systems (cs.SY) and mathematical optimization (cs.MA). Finally, the paper considers the growth rates of the number of users in the system, which can be related to performance evaluation (cs.PF).
